⚾️ Josh Winckowski tossed a scoreless 8th. Kenley Jansen slammed the door shut for his 15th save. 

⚾️ Kiké Hernández got things started for the offense with an RBI double. 1-for-4.

⚾️ Reese McGuire pulled off another clutch catcher’s interference. 1-for-2 with an RBI.

⚾️ Triston Casas went 1-for-3 with a 2-run ground rule double. Also walked once. 

⚾️ Big defensive night as Pablo Reyes (2), Jarren Duran, and Rafael Devers all made highlight plays.
